<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.7.3">
<l>teḷḷiya vāycciṟi yāṉnaṅkai kāḷuṟi mēlait taṭāni ṟainta</l>
<l>veḷḷi malaiyirun tālotta veṇṇeyai vāri viḻuṅki yiṭṭu</l>
<l>kaḷva ṉuṟaṅkukiṉ ṟāṉvantu kāṇmiṉkaḷ kaiyel lāmney vayiṟu</l>
<l>piḷḷai paramaṉṟiv vēḻula kumkoḷḷum pētaiyē ṉeṉcey kēṉō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Ladies, [this] child with clean lips, having scooped up and gulped down butter</l>
<l>Which filled the large pot high in the netting as if it was a white mountain,</l>
<l>The thief is [now] sleeping. Come see! [His] hands are all with ghee.</l>
<l>[His] stomach is not of a child’s body; it contains the seven worlds.</l>
<l rend="indent">What shall I, a simple [woman], do?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
